	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />VROM content: PPU$1234 = #$A5
<br />CPU writes PPU$1234 = #$A6
<br />CPU reads PPU$1234
<br />If it comes back as #$A6 then someone's obviously using VRAM instead of VROM. Authentic games have VROM; therefore someone's using a copier.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


